blogPost.excerpt:
Today TommyInnit, Wilbur Soot, Philza & Slimecicle have lots of fun with the Laser Eye Mod in Minecraft. It was properly mental.

STREAMING ON THE DREAM SMP - https://www.twitch.tv/tommyinnit​ 

Edited by Big Man Editor Larry @TalentLacking 

@Wilbur Soot @Ph1LzA @Slimecicle 

Follow my Twitter - @tommyinnit

Follow my Instagram - @tommyinnitt

Today Me, Wilbur Soot, Slimecicle, & Philza Minecraft install the Laser Eye Mod in Minecraft 1.16.4! Even though I had a Minecraft War with Dream on the Dream Team SMP Minecraft Server today Wilbur Soot went crazy and he is just hilarious and we had lots of laughs. This was so fun, awesome, poggers and cool! This Minecraft Mod uses the Laser Eye Plugin which makes the game so fun and cool but not Colorblind like GeorgeNotFound - thank god! I Love Minecraft fun. 

The Funniest Minecraft Video Ever with New Funny Mods makes Minecraft 1.16.4 even funnier & hilarious! It is lots of fun and laughs :) 

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin but it is me and my good friends playing the NEW FUNNIEST MINECRAFT MOD EVER!!! POG CHAMP!!!

I copy pasted that entire description from the previous video hahahahah

localize.title: TommyInnit - 镭射眼Model独家爆笑时刻。
localize.description:
今天 TommyInnit, Wilbur Soot, Philza & Slimecicle 有很多有趣的激光眼修改在威廉与。这是适当的精神。

串流上的梦想SMP - https://www.twitch.tv/tommyinnit 

编辑：大人物编辑拉里@人才匮乏 

@Wilbur Soot @Ph1LzA @Slimecicle 

关注我的微博 - @tommyinnit

关注我的Instagram - @tommyinnitt。

今天我, Wilbur Soot, Slimecicle, & Philza Minecraft 在 Minecraft 1.16.4 中安装激光眼 Mod! 尽管我今天在梦之队SMP Minecraft服务器上与Dream进行了一场Minecraft战争，但Wilbur Soot却疯了，他实在是太搞笑了，我们笑得很开心。这是如此有趣，真棒，poggers和酷! 这个Minecraft Mod使用激光眼插件，这使得游戏如此有趣和酷，但不像GeorgeNotFound那样的色盲-感谢上帝! 我爱Minecraft的乐趣。

有史以来最有趣的Minecraft视频与新的有趣的Mods使Minecraft 1.16.4更有趣&搞笑! 这是很多的乐趣和笑声:) 

不是Minecraft，但水上升或Minecraft，但熔岩上升，或任何其他但这样的挑战。这是一个速度运行/速度运行的Minecraft对杀手/刺客，但它是我和我的好朋友玩新的最有趣的MINECRAFT MOD有史以来！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！）。POG CHAMP!!!

我复制粘贴了整个描述，从以前的视频哈哈哈哈哈
